";i:638;s:339:"<ul ><li> The strangler in <em><a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/FamilyGuy' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/FamilyGuy'>Family Guy</a></em> episode "Fat Guy Strangler" murders fat guys because when he was a child, he walked in on his mother with Jackie Gleason.
